---
title: Public Tours
description: Join a public Land Shark Tour in Santa Barbara — a 90-minute amphibious adventure through the city and into the Pacific Ocean. View ticket prices, schedule, and tour departure information.
keywords: Santa Barbara public tours, Land Shark Tours tickets, Santa Barbara tour prices, amphibious tour schedule Santa Barbara, things to do Santa Barbara
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}

  {% include "components/page-hero.njk" %}

  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16 bg-teal-50 -mt-2">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6">

      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 items-start">

        <!-- Left sidebar: leaf cards -->
        <div class="hidden lg:flex flex-col gap-5 w-80 shrink-0">

          <!-- Vessels card -->
          <a href="{{ "/vessels/" | url }}" class="group flex overflow-hidden text-white bg-navy relative transition-all min-h-[160px]" style="border-radius: 25px 3px 99px 3px;">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-40 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="{{ "/assets/images/boat-1.jpg" | url }}" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="px-5 py-5">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-xl mb-2">Our Vessels</h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-90">Meet the amphibious craft that takes you from street to sea.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy-900 flex items-center justify-center -translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-transform duration-300">
              <span class="font-heading text-2xl text-white">Learn More &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- FAQ card -->
          <a href="{{ "/faq/" | url }}" class="group flex overflow-hidden text-white bg-teal relative transition-all min-h-[160px]" style="border-radius: 25px 3px 99px 3px;">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-40 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="{{ "/assets/images/santa-barbara.jpg" | url }}" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div class="px-5 py-5">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-xl mb-2">FAQ</h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-90">Got questions? We've got answers about tickets, timing, and more.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy-900 flex items-center justify-center -translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-transform duration-300">
              <span class="font-heading text-2xl text-white">View FAQ &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

        </div>

        <!-- Right: main content -->
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">

          <div class="mb-10">
            <span class="inline-block bg-teal text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest px-5 py-2" style="border-radius: 79px 15px 79px 15px;">Voted Best City &amp; Harbor Tour — Top 10 Things to Do in California</span>
          </div>

          <div class="grid gap-6 mb-10 md:grid-cols-3">

            <!-- Ticket Prices -->
            <div class="bg-navy-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-6">
              <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-4">Ticket Prices</h2>
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-navy-100">
                <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-3">
                  <span>Adult</span><span class="font-bold text-coral-300">$45</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-3">
                  <span>Children Under 10</span><span class="font-bold text-coral-300">$30</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between">
                  <span>Children Under 2 (on lap)</span><span class="font-bold text-teal-300">Free</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Schedule -->
            <div class="bg-teal-50 border border-teal-100 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-navy mb-4">Schedule</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Click "View Calendar" to see available tour days and times.</p>
              <a href="https://book.{{ client.bookingDomain }}.com/{{ client.rgPath }}/reservations/calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-teal">
                View Calendar
              </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Tour Departure -->
            <div class="bg-navy-50 border border-navy-100 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-navy mb-4">Tour Departure</h2>
              <address class="not-italic text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <p>{{ client.address.street }}</p>
                <p>{{ client.address.city }}, {{ client.address.state }} {{ client.address.zip }}</p>
              </address>
            </div>

          </div>

          <p class="mb-10 text-sm text-gray-500 italic">All tours are subject to cancellations. Some tour times may not be available. Passenger minimums may apply.</p>

          <div class="space-y-5 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p>Start on land just west of Stearns Wharf, winding through Santa Barbara's historic streets — landmarks, architecture, and the stories behind the city that the world's rich and famous call home.</p>
            <p>Then we splash into the Pacific. Cruise past luxury yachts and fishing fleets, hear the maritime legends of Stearns Wharf, and keep your eyes open — sea lions, seals, dolphins, and even whales are regular guests.</p>

            <!-- Horizontal leaf CTA -->
            <div class="flex overflow-hidden w-full my-8" style="border-radius: 99px 5px 99px 5px; min-height: 200px;">
              <div class="w-1/2 shrink-0 relative">
                <img src="{{ "/assets/images/boat-1.jpg" | url }}" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover">
              </div>
              <div class="w-1/2 bg-blue-600 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-white text-center px-8 gap-4">
                <p class="font-heading text-2xl lg:text-3xl leading-snug">Ready for your Santa Barbara adventure?</p>
                <a href="https://book.{{ client.bookingDomain }}.com/{{ client.rgPath }}/reservations/calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">
                  Book Now
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p><strong>No paid endorsements. Ever.</strong> Our route is chosen entirely for your experience — no sponsored detours, no traffic-wasting pit stops, no restaurant recommendations we got paid to make. Just the best of Santa Barbara, unfiltered.</p>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-navy-900 text-white rounded-2xl px-6 py-5 mt-2">
              <span class="text-teal text-2xl shrink-0">&#9432;</span>
              <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed"><strong class="font-semibold">Good to know:</strong> We accept cash, Visa, Mastercard, and Amex. Plan to arrive at least 15 minutes before departure.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

{% endblock %}
